100    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
101        //Validate.isTrue(raw.length == props().size());
102        this.cargo = raw;
103        this.appSoftwareVersion = Bytes.readString(raw, 0, 18);
104        this.appSoftwarePartNumber = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18);
105        this.appSoftwarePartDashNumber = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 22);
106        this.appSoftwarePartRevisionNumber = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 26);
107        this.bootloaderVersion = Bytes.readString(raw, 30, 17);
108        this.bootloaderPartNumber = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 47);
109        if (raw.length == 60) {
110            this.bootloaderPartDashNumber = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 51);
111            this.bootloaderPartRevisionNumber = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 55);
112        }

174    public static byte[] buildCargo(String appSoftwareVersion, long appSoftwarePartNumber, long appSoftwareDashNumber, long appSoftwarePartRevisionNumber, String bootloaderVersion, long bootloaderPartNumber, Long bootloaderPartDashNumber, Long bootloaderPartRevisionNumber) {
175        return Bytes.combine(
176            Bytes.writeString(appSoftwareVersion, 18),
177            Bytes.toUint32(appSoftwarePartNumber), 
178            Bytes.toUint32(appSoftwareDashNumber), 
179            Bytes.toUint32(appSoftwarePartRevisionNumber), 
180            Bytes.writeString(bootloaderVersion, 17),
181            Bytes.toUint32(bootloaderPartNumber),
182                (bootloaderPartDashNumber == null && bootloaderPartRevisionNumber == null) ?
183                    new byte[0] : Bytes.combine(
184                        Bytes.toUint32(bootloaderPartDashNumber),
185                        Bytes.toUint32(bootloaderPartRevisionNumber)));
186    }
